en\":\"Trim mode extracts a single clip. Split mode cuts at multiple time markers, producing separate files for each segment.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Video Preview\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Preview your video and scrub to the exact timestamp before cutting. Verify start and end points visually.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"100% Private\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"All processing happens in your browser using WebAssembly. Your files never leave your device.\"}]]}]]}]\n20:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-8\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L2b\",null,{}]}]\n21:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"my-8 flex justify-center\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L17\",null,{\"slot\":\"mid-content\"}]}]\n22:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"prose prose-sm dark:prose-invert max-w-none\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L2c\",null,{\"className\":\"my-8\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"not-prose mb-10\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Free Video Trimmer — Cut & Split Video Files Online\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"The Free Video Trimmer lets you cut video files to a specific time range or split them into multiple segments at custom time markers — all directly in your browser. No sign-up, no uploads, no watermarks, no file size limits. Powered by ffmpeg.wasm with stream copy mode for near-instant cuts and zero quality loss.\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Features\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 space-y-2 text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Instant stream copy\"}],\" — Uses ffmpeg's\",\" \",[\"$\",\"code\",null,{\"children\":\"-c copy\"}],\" mode. No re-encoding means near-instant processing and zero quality loss, even for large video files.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Trim mode\"}],\" — Extract a single clip by entering a start and end time. Perfect for pulling highlights from gameplay, cutting intros from recordings, or grabbing a scene from a movie.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Split mode\"}],\" — Add multiple time markers and split the video into separate segments. Great for breaking a long recording into chapters or extracting multiple clips at once.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Video preview\"}],\" — Watch and scrub through your video before cutting. Verify your timestamps visually to get precise results.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Flexible time input\"}],\" — Enter time as seconds (90), MM:SS (1:30), or HH:MM:SS (1:02:30). Decimal seconds supported for precision.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"100% client-side\"}],\" — Uses ffmpeg.wasm (WebAssembly). Your files never leave your device. No server uploads, no privacy concerns.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"How to Trim a Video\"}],[\"$\",\"ol\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 space-y-2 text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"1. Add a file\"}],\" — Drag and drop a video file into the upload area, or click to browse. MP4, WebM, MOV, AVI, and MKV are supported.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"2. Preview\"}],\" — Use the built-in player to scrub to the exact timestamps you want to cut.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"3. Choose mode\"}],\" — Click \",[\"$\",\"em\",null,{\"children\":\"Trim\"}],\" to extract a single clip, or \",[\"$\",\"em\",null,{\"children\":\"Split\"}],\" to cut at multiple markers.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"4. Enter times\"}],\" — For Trim mode, set the start and end time. For Split mode, add one or more time markers where you want to cut.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"5. Process & Download\"}],\" — Click the action button. Stream copy mode makes this fast regardless of file length. Download your clip(s) when done.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Video Trimmer vs. Video Editor\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 overflow-x-auto\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"table\",null,{\"className\":\"w-full text-sm\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"thead\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"tr\",null,{\"className\":\"border-b border-border\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"th\",null,{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 text-left font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Feature\"}],[\"$\",\"th\",null,{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 text-left font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Video Trimmer\"}],[\"$\",\"th\",null,{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 text-left font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Adobe Premiere Pro\"}]]}]}],\"$L2d\"]}]}],\"$L2e\",\"$L2f\",\"$L30\"]}]\n23:[\"$\",\"script\",\"script-0\",{\"src\":\"/_next/static/chunks/0dv~2kaq5i26t.js\",\"async\":true,\"nonce\":\"$undefined\"}]\n24:[\"$\",\"$L31\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$29\",null,{\"name\":\"Next.MetadataOutlet\",\"children\":\"$@32\"}]}]\n2d:[\"$\",\"tbody\",null,{\"className\":\"text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"tr\",null,{\"className\":\"border-b border-border\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"class