c\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"tr\",null,{\"className\":\"border-b border-border\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium\",\"children\":\"Install required\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4\",\"children\":\"No\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4\",\"children\":\"Yes (large download)\"}]]}]]}]\n2e:[[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-labelledby\":\"tool-insights-tips\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"tool-insights-tips\",\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":[\"Tips from Building \",\"the Video Trimmer\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Notes from designing and testing this tool — what we kept in mind, the edge cases we worked around, and the small choices that make the difference between a tool that ships and one that breaks on real input.\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"Stream-copy trims finish in seconds, not minutes\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\",\"key\":\"1gvzjb\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M9 18h6\",\"key\":\"x1upvd\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M10 22h4\",\"key\":\"ceow96\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Stream-copy trims finish in seconds, not minutes\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"When the trim aligns to a keyframe (typically every 1–2 seconds in H.264), ffmpeg can stream-copy the cut without re-encoding. The tool prefers stream copy when possible — that's why some trims finish almost instantly.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Trim slightly wider, then re-trim if needed\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$2e:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Trim slightly wider, then re-trim if needed\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Frame-accurate trims sometimes need a couple-frame buffer to avoid cutting mid-syllable on speech or mid-motion on action. It's easier to widen now and re-trim than to recover lost content later.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Scrub to confirm the cut points before exporting\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$2e:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Scrub to confirm the cut points before exporting\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"The timeline shows where the cuts land. Scrub through both endpoints before exporting — a cut that looks right at second 5.0 may need to be at 5.4 to land at the natural pause.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Keep the original file until the trim is verified\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$2e:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Keep the original file until the trim is verified\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Trimming exports a new file; the source is untouched. Keep the source until you've played back the trimmed output end-to-end and confirmed the cuts are right.\"}]]}]]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-labelledby\":\"tool-insights-mistakes\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"tool-insights-mistakes\",\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Common Mistakes to Avoid\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"Trying frame-accurate trims on long-GOP MP4 with stream copy\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[\"$L33\",\"$L34\"]}],\"$L35\",\"$L36\"]}]]}],\"$L37\"]\n2f:[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Frequently Asked Questions\"}]\n30:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 space-y-4 text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Why is trimming so fast?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1\",\"children\":[\"The trimmer uses ffmpeg's stream copy mode (\",[\"$\",\"code\",null,{\"children\":\"-c copy\"}],\"), which copies the video and audio data without decoding or re-encoding. The only work is reading the container, copying the relevant packets, and writing a new container. This makes it orders of magnitude faster than re-encoding.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Are the cuts frame-exact?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1\",\"children\":\"Stream copy mode cuts at the nearest keyframe (I-frame). For most videos encoded with keyframes every 1–2 seconds, the cut point will be within a second of your requested time. If you need frame-exact cuts, you would need to re-encode the video, which our Video Converter can help with.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Can I trim very large video files?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1\",\"children\":\"Yes, but keep in mind that the entire file must be loaded into browser memory via WebAssembly. Files up to ~2 GB work well on most modern machines with 8+ GB RAM. For very large files, the loading step may take a moment, but the actual cutting is still fast.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Does trimming add a watermark?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1\",\"children\":\"No. The output is an exact copy of the original video data — nothing is added, removed, or modified. There are no watermarks, logos, or branding of any kind.\"}]]}]]}]\n33:[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\",\"key\":\"wmoenq\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M12 9v4\",\"key\":\"juzpu7\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M12 17h.01\",\"key\":\"p32p05\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\"}]\n34:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Trying frame-accurate trims on long-GOP MP4 with stream copy\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Stream copy cuts only at keyframes. For frame-accurate cuts inside a GOP, the tool falls back to re-encoding — that's expected, not a bug. It just takes longer.\"}]]}]\n35:[\"$\",\"li\",\"Forgetting to set both start AND end\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L5\",null