he exact timestamps you want to cut.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"3. Choose mode\"}],\" — Click \",[\"$\",\"em\",null,{\"children\":\"Trim\"}],\" to extract a single clip, or \",[\"$\",\"em\",null,{\"children\":\"Split\"}],\" to cut at multiple markers.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"4. Enter times\"}],\" — For Trim mode, set the start and end time. For Split mode, add one or more time markers where you want to cut.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"5. Process & Download\"}],\" — Click the action button. Stream copy mode makes this fast regardless of file length. Download your clip(s) when done.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Video Trimmer vs. Video Editor\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 overflow-x-auto\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"table\",null,{\"className\":\"w-full text-sm\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"thead\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"tr\",null,{\"className\":\"border-b border-border\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"th\",null,{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 text-left font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Feature\"}],[\"$\",\"th\",null,{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 text-left font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Video Trimmer\"}],[\"$\",\"th\",null,{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 text-left font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Adobe Premiere Pro\"}]]}]}],\"$L14\"]}]}],\"$L15\",\"$L16\",\"$L17\"]}]\nd:[\"$\",\"script\",\"script-0\",{\"src\":\"/_next/static/chunks/0dv~2kaq5i26t.js\",\"async\":true}]\ne:[\"$\",\"$L18\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$19\",null,{\"name\":\"Next.MetadataOutlet\",\"children\":\"$@1a\"}]}]\n14:[\"$\",\"tbody\",null,{\"className\":\"text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"tr\",null,{\"className\":\"border-b border-border\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"className\":\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium\",\"children\":\"Price\"}],[\"$\",\"td\",null,{\"className\":\"py-